Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's fifth league match.
Team Orange vs Team Blue. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.

The rules are set: (1) Three tags per team, per round.
(2) Three 12-minute non-scripted wrestling rounds. (3)
Last round consists of the winners tying up,
dominating, humiliating, and brutally fucking the
losers. IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE!

Team Black: Is un-defeated in Tag Team action (2-0). However Black has suffered a set back this week as Adrianna Nicole is injured and Black is compelled to go with a substitute.

Team Red: Team red has won and lost by the narrowest of margins (1-1). This week however they look to capitalize on Blacks inability to put there best team on the mat.
